llboard\"/>}}\n{{Certification Table Summary}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Worldwide|nocert=true|salesamount=2,500,000|salesref=<ref name=\"WW sales\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.org/downloads/GMR2017.pdf|title=Global Music Report 2017|publisher=[[IFPI]] |date=April 25, 2017 |accessdate=July 8, 2019 }}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom}}\n\n== Release history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|+ List of release dates, showing region, format(s), label(s) and reference(s).\n! scope=\"col\" | Region\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n! scope=\"col\" | Format(s)\n! scope=\"col\" | Label(s)\n! scope=\"col\" | {{abbr|Ref.|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\" | Various<!--Impossible to source release to the entire populated land mass of the planet.-->\n| {{Start date|mf=yes|2016|04|23}}\n| [[Streaming media|Streaming]] {{small|([[Tidal (service)|Tidal]] exclusive)}}\n| rowspan=\"3\"| {{Flatlist |\n* [[Parkwood Entertainment|Parkwood]]\n* [[Columbia Records|Columbia]]\n}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"LemonadeCredits\">{{cite web|url=http://listen.tidal.com/album/59727856|title=Lemonade / Beyonc\u00e9|publisher=Tidal|date=April 23, 2016|accessdate=April 23, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Start date|mf=yes|2016|04|24}}\n| [[Music download|Digital download]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"LemonadeTidalDownload\">{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2016/04/24/beyonce-lemonade-tidal-itunes/83471916/|title=Beyonc\u00e9's 'Lemonade' hits music retailers tonight|last=Ryan|first=Patrick|work=USA Today|date=April 24, 2016|accessdate=April 24, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Start date|mf=yes|2016|05|06}}\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[Compact Disc|CD]]+[[DVD]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sonymusic.pl/albumy/beyonce-lemonade|title=Beyonc\u00e9 \u2013 \"Lemonade\"|publisher=[[Sony Music Entertainment Poland]]|language=Polish|accessdate=May 14, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B